		<!-- message -->
		<div>Here's another version.<br />
<br />
I've added another 20 minute timer, this time you set it to all-white and the red bar moves across... when it's all-red 20 minutes have passed.  The catch is that it takes another 20 minutes for the timer to transition back to all-white.  This is a bit more similar to Arista-style timers so people might like it better.<br />
<br />
On this one the slider ratio is 4-to-1.  That means each movement of the slider advances the timer by 40 seconds.  The other three 20-minute timers with the small bars have a resolution of 24 seconds.</div>
		<!-- / message -->
	
		
